&lt;h2&gt;Cable Industry Price Survey (Form 333) Electronic Filing System&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The 2015 cable industry price survey has been converted into a web-based survey.&amp;#160; Users must access the survey questionnaire through the &amp;lt;&lt;a title="Electronic Filing" href="https://specialreports.fcc.gov/mb/Form333/"&gt;Electronic Filing&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt; link on this page.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following link leads to detailed instructions for accessing, completing, and submitting your completed questionnaire &amp;lt;&lt;a title="FCC Form 333 Instructions" href="http://hraunfoss.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/DA-15-1152A2.pdf"&gt;Order and Instructions&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h2&gt;Form 333 Questions&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please address any questions to &lt;a href="mailto:cablesurvey@fcc.gov"&gt;cablesurvey@fcc.gov&lt;/a&gt; or call (202) 418-2330 to speak to a member of the cable price survey Team.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;h2&gt;FCC Registration Numbers&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Filers now need to have an FCC Registration Number (FRN) and a password in order to make the Form 333 filing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;fieldset class="fieldgroup group-dates"&gt;&lt;legend&gt;Dates&lt;/legend&gt;&lt;div class="field field-type-date field-field-updated-date"&gt;
